Sub-Advisor
Since 1994, Portfolio Advisors has managed private equity, private real estate and private credit investments while also seeking to minimize risk through prudent diversification and the careful selection of high quality investment managers. The firm invests on behalf of their clients and funds through primary partnerships, secondary purchases, co-investments and direct investments. Portfolio Advisors manages over $36 billion in assets, and has a global presence with offices in the U.S., Europe, and Asia.

